channel.title: A Moparscape Downloads Tutorial download
channel.description:
I was sitting looking through some of the models and thought why not make a [i]Moparscape Downloads Tutorial[/i] section download What i did is copied some of the tutorials and alot of the downloads and put them into a small Power Point Panel.
There aint much tutorials but there are many downloads.
Sorry about no pictures but whats the point if you're downloading tutorials and other downloads?
So enough Jibba Jabba heres the download link. http://uppit.com/v/LTENOZZ8
Trust me about this download its 100% trustable, i dont do virus i dont do trojans. Heck i dont even know how to add them.
[center]Please dont be harsh to me im not really a tutorial or download giver. Im more of a tutorial and download reciever.[/center]
